{"tid":1277422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我都想好似啲人咁撚大膽","createTime":"2019-07-02T07:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T12:23:44.000Z","uid":88323,"like":153,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7345b0e2b1d8a778488af8c883b26dc9c5d580b7","tid":1277422,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:39:38.000Z","msg":"尋朝一早訓左 發夢發到夜晚10點幾<br />\n其實大部分時間都係係天橋/公園/馬路個啲位遠望<br />\n最多都係幫手搬下物資 起下哄<br />\n<br />\n就訓醒個陣 突然有啲想行前少少 <br />\n就膽粗粗行左去近煲底嘅位置 <br />\n一行到埋去 啲氣氛完全唔撚同<br />\n<br />\n自問比較細膽 其實就咁企個度已經好緊張<br />\n前前後後應該留左係個度1個鐘左右<br />\n好似每一下都就快有嘢要發生咁<br />\n有兩三次 前面啲人突然大叫「走啊」再向海邊方向跑  (雖然跑左兩三步又有人話無事 唔使驚）<br />\n真係嚇到我標屎<br />\n<br />\n今日再見到好多消息先發現 <br />\n好多比我行得更前嘅人其實都係啲學生哥甚至妹妹仔 <br />\n反觀自己大人大者 全程縮到龜咁<br />\n一諗起就覺得自己好無用<br />\n<br />\n有無人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3124e43b0766b7af3c0d15d45943534c71780bb9","tid":1277422,"uid":20914,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n每次返到去都會問自己點解唔行前啲"},{"pid":"47a579efe1faaa31cd49b9a45bb2bf309d0b9643","tid":1277422,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bb2f6dfbe7823ed1b7fd36d43bddf1d63e6672","tid":1277422,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:45:54.000Z","msg":"下次預埋你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8623ba1e348f33f0de19c8cbb2f11a32540dfb","tid":1277422,"uid":88323,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:48:13.000Z","msg":"行到接近最前 同係外圍個感覺真係差好遠"},{"pid":"b9abf46d448d235474769263f437fa99d8d4243c","tid":1277422,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b26e8d4e55614eb6bc41f4e75c4c6b92ec9ccf","tid":1277422,"uid":7716,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:51:16.000Z","msg":"當你企到最前 其實就唔會驚<br />\n因為身邊陪你嘅都係手足<br />\n要走 都係一齊走"},{"pid":"7b2194f336db50f340f32706d7b44d8a4685fdb9","tid":1277422,"uid":37689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"發夢要有基本裝 唔係實驚"},{"pid":"d288abe768be6b30fd88f95c978fac3a9b1a6bba","tid":1277422,"uid":164368,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:55:10.000Z","msg":"頭先係小巴有個阿叔話，做事量力而為，如果你只<br />\n<br />\n係靠大膽入去，冇裝備同埋心理準備，希望你哋唔<br />\n<br />\n好行得太前，你咁做有機會變成前線負累。<br />\n<br />\n當然如果有氣有力亦明白後果，唔怕企前少少，齊<br />\n<br />\n上齊落，一個都不能少："},{"pid":"e931455e52a81c58eb69faf4c57004d50acaa03b","tid":1277422,"uid":47303,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:55:33.000Z","msg":"有人叫走真係睇清楚咩事先好走<br />\n你老味都未知咩事成班走到冇雷公咁遠"},{"pid":"103c6cd0b726b510d45cabce8e72be2f1eeadea5","tid":1277422,"uid":172733,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"最on9 係full gear企好遠同埋叫極唔好留斜路d on9 仔"},{"pid":"5d65d51954e950a8862a55013c269aad1f57ae7c","tid":1277422,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:56:31.000Z","msg":"真係希望人人都操下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197ac482ae99c505007e4a3dd0cd599aff991d84","tid":1277422,"uid":88323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e931455e52a81c58eb69faf4c57004d50acaa03b","tid":1277422,"uid":47303,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:55:33.000Z","msg":"有人叫走真係睇清楚咩事先好走<br />\n你老味都未知咩事成班走到冇雷公咁遠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"其實有無人知點解無啦啦叫走 又可以係10秒內話無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係個啲情況 成千幾二千人（或者更多）向住你跑 其實好難唔跑埋一份"},{"pid":"b9194e2efbac5eaedc76ac012c38048ad6f244cb","tid":1277422,"uid":76094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:58:54.000Z","msg":"有岀到力已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各有各本份姐"},{"pid":"d3b1534f94055f011c77d57251408e7c4816a21a","tid":1277422,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:02:52.000Z","msg":"真，尋晚發夢拎咗啲物資去到金鐘之後一直都喺外圍幫手。<br />\n係有去過煲底，個氣氛真係好唔同，全場叫&ldquo;一齊走！&rdquo;真係好感動。<br />\n但我全身上下只係得個好過冇嘅醫生口罩（唔想攞物資站嘅嘢，要留畀更有需要嘅人），真係唔敢衝入去/衝上前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好撚細膽，對唔住，下次出嚟會加強自己裝備先。各位都要記得著齊裝先好上前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dcb01f39ccce5c0e9cd04b2e43750139c40010f","tid":1277422,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d65d51954e950a8862a55013c269aad1f57ae7c","tid":1277422,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:56:31.000Z","msg":"真係希望人人都操下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:07:12.000Z","msg":"起碼做到30下掌上壓先准企前線，因為對面個個都50下..."},{"pid":"97b5cd2c64b526690245cf090b6ddaf8c51aa75e","tid":1277422,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5d65d51954e950a8862a55013c269aad1f57ae7c","tid":1277422,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:56:31.000Z","msg":"真係希望人人都操下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:12:10.000Z","msg":"就係自己有操開先更加覺得自己無用"},{"pid":"37f8965a8520ea80526dba83b7595ae412e0f790","tid":1277422,"uid":122676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:15:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92cf56ee7c6840dba777e9d7288f3ce4e6c172af","tid":1277422,"uid":215794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7345b0e2b1d8a778488af8c883b26dc9c5d580b7","tid":1277422,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:39:38.000Z","msg":"尋朝一早訓左 發夢發到夜晚10點幾<br />\n其實大部分時間都係係天橋/公園/馬路個啲位遠望<br />\n最多都係幫手搬下物資 起下哄<br />\n<br />\n就訓醒個陣 突然有啲想行前少少 <br />\n就膽粗粗行左去近煲底嘅位置 <br />\n一行到埋去 啲氣氛完全唔撚同<br />\n<br />\n自問比較細膽 其實就咁企個度已經好緊張<br />\n前前後後應該留左係個度1個鐘左右<br />\n好似每一下都就快有嘢要發生咁<br />\n有兩三次 前面啲人突然大叫「走啊」再向海邊方向跑  (雖然跑左兩三步又有人話無事 唔使驚）<br />\n真係嚇到我標屎<br />\n<br />\n今日再見到好多消息先發現 <br />\n好多比我行得更前嘅人其實都係啲學生哥甚至妹妹仔 <br />\n反觀自己大人大者 全程縮到龜咁<br />\n一諗起就覺得自己好無用<br />\n<br />\n有無人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"你嘅承受能力會慢慢提升的<br />\n<br />\n最重要嘅係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你要清楚知道自己嘅能耐</span><br />\n例如 跑路有多快？<br />\n跨障礙物的能力<br />\n被追究法律責任時的底線 等<br />\n<br />\n當你清楚知道以上種種後<br />\n你就會企前到一個啱你嘅企置<br />\n可以全身而退<br />\n甚至可以幫到其他人<br />\n亦唔會成為負纍<br />\n<br />\n前提係 你係自己一個<br />\n因為三兩成群圍威喂<br />\n會變得保守好多"},{"pid":"b114066deaf7a87cae28ac564d84af124f1c0524","tid":1277422,"uid":259820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:20:54.000Z","msg":"盡自己力就好，每人嘅覺悟同條底線都唔同，各司其職，多謝你為香港發咗場夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0675d4fe09cca2ea306db4b8db6b48233861741","tid":1277422,"uid":88323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92cf56ee7c6840dba777e9d7288f3ce4e6c172af","tid":1277422,"uid":215794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7345b0e2b1d8a778488af8c883b26dc9c5d580b7","tid":1277422,"uid":88323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:39:38.000Z","msg":"尋朝一早訓左 發夢發到夜晚10點幾<br />\n其實大部分時間都係係天橋/公園/馬路個啲位遠望<br />\n最多都係幫手搬下物資 起下哄<br />\n<br />\n就訓醒個陣 突然有啲想行前少少 <br />\n就膽粗粗行左去近煲底嘅位置 <br />\n一行到埋去 啲氣氛完全唔撚同<br />\n<br />\n自問比較細膽 其實就咁企個度已經好緊張<br />\n前前後後應該留左係個度1個鐘左右<br />\n好似每一下都就快有嘢要發生咁<br />\n有兩三次 前面啲人突然大叫「走啊」再向海邊方向跑  (雖然跑左兩三步又有人話無事 唔使驚）<br />\n真係嚇到我標屎<br />\n<br />\n今日再見到好多消息先發現 <br />\n好多比我行得更前嘅人其實都係啲學生哥甚至妹妹仔 <br />\n反觀自己大人大者 全程縮到龜咁<br />\n一諗起就覺得自己好無用<br />\n<br />\n有無人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"